videos.description: Following a wire-to-wire 56-53 win over Mississippi State, No. 18 Tennessee's Yves Pons explains how the Vols pulled away and "out-toughed" the Bulldogs.
videos.headline: Physicality helps Vols outlast 'great' MS State team
